@host = http://localhost:5000

### Health - full report
GET {{host}}/api/health

### Health - ping
GET {{host}}/api/health/ping

### Health - ASP.NET built-in
GET {{host}}/health

### Health - liveness
GET {{host}}/alive

### Diagnostics - masked config values
GET {{host}}/api/diag

### ─── Connect Five ──────────────────────────────────

### Get player stats (ConnectFive)
GET {{host}}/api/ConnectFive/players/TestPlayer/stats

### Save player stats (ConnectFive)
PUT {{host}}/api/ConnectFive/players/TestPlayer/stats
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "test-1",
  "playerName": "TestPlayer",
  "easy": { "wins": 3, "losses": 1, "draws": 0, "totalGames": 4, "winStreak": 2, "winRate": 0.75 },
  "medium": { "wins": 0, "losses": 0, "draws": 0, "totalGames": 0, "winStreak": 0, "winRate": 0 },
  "hard": { "wins": 0, "losses": 0, "draws": 0, "totalGames": 0, "winStreak": 0, "winRate": 0 },
  "totalWins": 3,
  "totalLosses": 1,
  "totalDraws": 0,
  "totalGames": 4,
  "winRate": 0.75,
  "overallWinRate": 0.75,
  "createdAt": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "updatedAt": "2026-02-15T00:00:00Z"
}

### Leaderboard (ConnectFive)
GET {{host}}/api/ConnectFive/statistics/leaderboard?limit=10

